divs: Sighting DetailsHi, My name is David Gubitosa and I live in Hillsborough NJ. I recently traveled to Ireland. I was taking pictures of the beautiful scenery and didn't notice anything pecuilar. This picture was taken on August 25 2005. When I got home from vacation I looked at the pictures on the TV.It was then that I noticed this object. I don't know what it is. I know that it's not a bird or plane. Were I was staying in Ireland is totally country. There are no airports, and the fields are filled with sheep and cows. When I blew up the picture with my digital camera the image gets dark and blurry. Please let me know what you think it might be. I was told by a photo lab that the image is definetly too big to be a bird The camera I used was a digital Canon Elph 4.0 megapixels
trends: there have been no other sightings in glen carain\tallow
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: I did not notice anything, until I got home and looked at the picture.
